## 15. Performance Considerations

### Build Time
- Static export is fast
- No server-side rendering
- Pre-rendered HTML

### Bundle Size
- Tree-shaking with Next.js
- Tailwind purges unused CSS
- Font Awesome CDN (not in bundle)
- Consider code splitting for future features

### Runtime Performance
- Client-side navigation (instant)
- Intersection Observer (efficient)
- CSS transitions (GPU accelerated)
- Optimized images with Next.js Image

### Optimization Opportunities
- Add `loading="lazy"` to images below fold
- Consider web font optimization
- Add service worker for offline (future)
- Implement code splitting for routes (future)

